  "original_title": "Kitchen & Bedroom commended for interior excellence at Laya Leisure",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kitchen & Bedroom commended for interior excellence at Laya Leisure",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kitchen & Bedroom Group CEO Dr. Mohammed Rushmi Sacquaff (left) with Defence Ministry Disaster Management Director General Rtd. Major General Sudantha Ranasinghe",
        "Kitchen & Bedroom, one of the preferred partner and leader in the industry providing total solutions in space planning and designing, was recently commended for its interior project carried out at Laya Leisure, a stunning hotel property situated amid lush tropical vegetation with spectacular views in Molkawa, Kurunegala managed by the Sri Lankan Army.",
        "Defence Ministry Disaster Management Director General Rtd. Major General Sudantha Ranasinghe extended his appreciation to Kitchen & Bedroom\u2019s Group CEO Dr. Mohammed Rushmi Sacquaff for his highly personalised and meticulous details of designing, architectural manufacturing and arranging all the shales, including the eye-catching colour combination and the superior quality of materials used during the project.",
        "Further, Major General Ranasinghe appraised Dr. Sacquaff\u2019s knowledge and experience for this advanced and unique thinking of the structure, professionalism and the timely delivery of the project. Dr. Sacquaff brings a wealth of expertise and contribution to the field of interior designing, equipped with a Doctorate in Interior Designing by the American National Business University, Delaware, USA.",
        "Dr. Sacquaff continues to lead Kitchen & Bedroom, which today is a sought-after interior planning and designing outfit, as its chief designing consultant across projects in addition to being the Group CEO. His knack for capturing and designing highly evolving living spaces blending the best of luxury, comfort and functionality is acknowledge by numerous clients. Dr. Sacquaff also mentors and leads a team of highly qualified interior designers, inspiring them with refined artistry and craftsmanship.",
        "Dr. Sacquaff believes in providing customers the best possible advice and solutions in optimising and realising their interior space, colour and style, guiding and taking them through every step of the project including consultations and 3D drawings and more advanced services such as colour balancing and lighting and electrical layout design, all free of charge.",
        "Kitchen & Bedroom recently also incepted its very own state-of-the-art quality-controlled manufacturing and assembling facility in Colombo equipped with German and Spain technology with ambitious plans to expand and enter to key export markets. Last year, Dr. Sacquaff was named \u2018Best CEO of the Year\u2019 at BIO Awards, was recently conferred as Master Project Manager (MPM) and designated as Fellow of the American Academy of Project Management (FAAPM)."
      ],
